  "texts": [
    "Recent advancements have seen a surge in the adoption of deep learning models for sentiment analysis.",
    "Researchers have employed diverse models, including but not limited to:",
    "• Long short-term memory (LSTM) (Day and Lin 2017),",
    "• Tree-LSTM (Tai et al. 2015),",
    "• Bidirectional long short-term memory (Bi-LSTM) (Wang et al. 2016d),"
  ]
}